I know

281
00:17:14,540 --> 00:17:15,400
it's you.

282
00:17:18,360 --> 00:17:20,300
Instructor Yi, why are you here?

283
00:17:23,170 --> 00:17:26,080
In addition to being
the physical art teacher of Faction 60,

284
00:17:26,080 --> 00:17:28,190
I'm also Sword Saint of Huaxiu.

285
00:17:28,710 --> 00:17:30,570
Sword Saint of Huaxiu?

286
00:17:30,830 --> 00:17:32,600
I've been observing for a long time.

287
00:17:32,860 --> 00:17:36,200
You are the heir I am looking for.

288
00:17:36,780 --> 00:17:39,430
Senior, are you mistaken?

289
00:17:39,640 --> 00:17:40,850
Impossible.

290
00:17:41,270 --> 00:17:46,680
You have the same aura as the powerhouse
who appeared in the Faction 60 last time.

291
00:17:46,890 --> 00:17:49,480
That's a powerful spiritual impulse.

292
00:17:49,270 --> 00:17:54,770
Raccoon Crispy Instant Noodle

293
00:17:50,850 --> 00:17:54,590
There was also a faint whiff
of pepper powder.

294
00:17:54,880 --> 00:17:55,560
What?

295
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:57,410
So far, Miss Sun,

296
00:17:57,520 --> 00:18:00,940
do you still say
that you don't know swordsmanship?

297
00:18:00,940 --> 00:18:04,840
Senior, do you want me to be the
disciple of Infinite Sword Faction?

298
00:18:05,610 --> 00:18:07,640
You're too powerful

299
00:18:07,640 --> 00:18:11,590
to be my disciple.

300
00:18:12,910 --> 00:18:14,610
Miss Sun, if you agree,

301
00:18:14,610 --> 00:18:17,490
you can be the new leader
of Infinite Sword Faction.

302
00:18:17,490 --> 00:18:18,620
What?

303
00:18:18,890 --> 00:18:20,330
Infinite Sword Faction

304
00:18:20,330 --> 00:18:22,680
will revive its name

305
00:18:22,920 --> 00:18:24,470
under your leadership.

306
00:18:24,470 --> 00:18:25,890
What?
